This torrent does not have the fan edition bonus cd for Darkly, Darkly Venus Aversa. The cd in this torrent is from the digipak and contains only 4 tracks. The fan edition has 8. Track listing for the true fan edition is:

1. Beast of Extermination 
2. Truth And Agony 
3. Adest Rosa Secreta Eros 
4. Mistress From The Sucking Pit 
5. Behind The Jagged Mountains 
6. The Cult Of Venus Aversa (demo) 
7. The Nun With The Astral Habit (demo) 
8. Deceiving Eyes (demo) 

This is a great torrent tho. One of the most complete Cradle discogs I have seen.
